name: Nothing In The Way - Ludum Dare 45 (COMPO)
name_original: Nothing In The Way - Ludum Dare 45 (COMPO)
description:
Nothing In The Way is a puzzle/plateformer made in less than 48 hours for the Ludum Dare 45 Game Jam(COMPO). 

Game Design, Level Design, Programmation, Graphics, Music and SFX by Jimmy Gagnon-Vézina.
